<code class="lh-copy">
  pressing <b>r</b> allows you to replace the character under the cursor with whatever character you press next.<br><br>
  pressing <b>R</b> will enter you into replace mode, so each character you type replaces the one your cursor is over, until you hit <esc>
</code>

